{
  "texts": [
    "First, the application for Android was disassembled, and its opcode sequences were retrieved for analysis.",
    "An opcode embedding layer received one-hot vectors of opcode instructions.",
    "The embedding layer enabled the CNN network to gather opcode semantics.",
    "Abstract characteristics were extracted using convolution layers.",
    "Moreover, a max-pooling layer after each convolution layer selected the most appropriate malware-detecting opcode sequence."
  ]
}